{"tid":2298472,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"蘋民直擊｜旺角建興大廈嫖客染疫 全副保護袍警員登記單身男身份證地址 多間鳳樓仍營業","createTime":"2020-11-24T05:31:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T07:50:02.000Z","uid":5195,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"87b43d5f819368a9628afa29aa70dd87a7f66b07","tid":2298472,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:31:16.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎第四波疫情趨惡化，昨日8宗源頭不明個案之一的35歲男患者，有報道指他向當局承認，本月8日曾到旺角亞皆老街與花園街交界的建興大廈光顧鳳樓，但報稱記不起曾到訪的樓層，再次惹起爆發召妓群組的恐慌。有讀者向《蘋果》表示，周日凌晨途經建興大廈時，目睹多名身穿全副保護裝備的警員在上址「駐守」，在建興大廈出入口截查離開大廈的男子，登記他們的身份證及住址資料，疑為有助日後有需要時作出追查。至今日，上述大廈內多間鳳樓仍然營業，但有鳳樓貼出通告指若顧客不戴口罩「恕不招待」，有負責大廈清潔的工人則指已提供樣本作武漢肺炎病毒快速測試，心情難禁不安。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201124/VBA4DAJSX5BW3GP7P5OR5JFWR4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201124%2FVBA4DAJSX5BW3GP7P5OR5JFWR4%2F&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaCvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=8de3ebf2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201124%2FVBA4DAJSX5BW3GP7P5OR5JFWR4%2F&h=8cc2731e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201124/VBA4DAJSX5BW3GP7P5OR5JFWR4/</a>"},{"pid":"4c7e304433088d9bf2d14321b68edc1ffb4ab3a9","tid":2298472,"uid":11291,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:34:10.000Z","msg":"班雞蟲無得買球拍了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e9e522f58bfe4dd0876334884b6509d1b7352b","tid":2298472,"uid":353804,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:36:26.000Z","msg":"好心去富士啦"},{"pid":"7d54adab9c9c24c5b230acce3d0217160a93b1d9","tid":2298472,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:37:05.000Z","msg":"利群樓表示笑而不語"},{"pid":"51860e057e00154bc5fc2d4ee6904c1b464dbdba","tid":2298472,"uid":155815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c7e304433088d9bf2d14321b68edc1ffb4ab3a9","tid":2298472,"uid":11291,"like":6,"